title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Start from scratch - Airbus A330
description:
In this how to we are going to look how we can start the Airbus A330 from scratch including programming the MCDU.
We programmed the flight using the build-in flightplanner from MSFS 2020 since no Simbrief integration is available for this aircraft.

You can download the Airbus A330 from the site below:

https://aircraft.projectmegapack.com/A330Version0.2.zip

Keep in mind this aircraft it not compatible with the A32NX mod currently.
